        "title": "Project Preferences",
        "excerpt":"Go to your Account Settings to change your projects preferences. Note that these settings will only be visible to yourself.   image.jpeg   Collapse all subtask by default  If checked, when you switch to different projects, all the tasks would be collapsed to the root task by default.   Put favorited tasks to My Tasks  This is checked by default. Uncheck it, then the favorite tasks won’t be shown in the My Tasks section.   Assign to myself automatically when creating a task  If checked, the newly created tasks will be assigned to yourself automatically.  ","categories": ["project","preferences"],
